  <h1>Pavilion Damansara - Web Asset Requirements</h1>
  <p>Please follow the exact folder structures and naming conventions below to ensure seamless integration into the website. Maintain transparent backgrounds (.png) for floorplans if possible, or clean solid white/black backgrounds (.jpg).</p>
